             were indicted for <rs id="t18160403-55-off280" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18160403-55-off280" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160403-55-off280" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160403-55-cd281" type="crimeDate">9th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160403-55-off280 t18160403-55-cd281"></join>, twenty-two yards of printed cotton, value 2l. 10s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160403-55-victim501" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Houlbrooke
                        <interp inst="t18160403-55-victim501" type="surname" value="Houlbrooke"></interp>
